{"id":1060,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":26,"title":"Conversation 16","subtitle":"Office Expansion Progress","level":"B1","parts":13,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-16.1060/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/0-conversation-16.mp3","transcript":"Have you two taken a look at the progress they've made upstairs on the office expansion?\nIt looks great!\nI know!\nI can't believe it!\nAnd the offices up there have amazing views of the city.\nI wonder which division will move up there when it's finished.\nI heard it's the research department.\nAh, because they have the most people.\nProbably.\nI'd love to have an office on that floor, though.\nYeah.\nWell, the company must be making good money if they're adding that space!\nI think you're right, there!","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:59:45","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Have you two taken a look at the progress they've made upstairs on the office expansion?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/1.mp3","time_start":0.22,"time_end":4.83},{"position":2,"content":"It looks great!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/2.mp3","time_start":4.83,"time_end":6.02},{"position":3,"content":"I know!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/3.mp3","time_start":6.16,"time_end":7.28},{"position":4,"content":"I can't believe it!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/4.mp3","time_start":7.28,"time_end":8.59},{"position":5,"content":"And the offices up there have amazing views of the city.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/5.mp3","time_start":8.59,"time_end":12.23},{"position":6,"content":"I wonder which division will move up there when it's finished.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/6.mp3","time_start":12.32,"time_end":15.52},{"position":7,"content":"I heard it's the research department.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/7.mp3","time_start":15.52,"time_end":18.15},{"position":8,"content":"Ah, because they have the most people.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/8.mp3","time_start":18.15,"time_end":20.22},{"position":9,"content":"Probably.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/9.mp3","time_start":20.41,"time_end":21.51},{"position":10,"content":"I'd love to have an office on that floor, though.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/10.mp3","time_start":21.51,"time_end":24.07},{"position":11,"content":"Yeah.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/11.mp3","time_start":24.07,"time_end":24.98},{"position":12,"content":"Well, the company must be making good money if they're adding that space!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/12.mp3","time_start":24.98,"time_end":28.58},{"position":13,"content":"I think you're right, there!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-16-2023-09-11-16-38-09/13.mp3","time_start":28.58,"time_end":30.11}]}